17namespace webrtc {
18
19DefaultNetEqFactory::DefaultNetEqFactory() = default;
20DefaultNetEqFactory::~DefaultNetEqFactory() = default;
21
22std::unique_ptr<NetEq> DefaultNetEqFactory::CreateNetEq(
23 const NetEq::Config& config,
24 const rtc::scoped_refptr<AudioDecoderFactory>& decoder_factory,
25 Clock* clock) const {
26 return std::make_unique<NetEqImpl>(
27 config, NetEqImpl::Dependencies(config, clock, decoder_factory,
28 controller_factory_));
29}
